Always super slow. Order from the mobile app all the time. The order should be done by 5-7 minutes but I walk in and it takes another 5 minutes to get my order done. Sometimes I order my order when I’m 10 minutes away and it still isn’t ready. The most annoying part is, I order these orders usually around 6 pm when no one is in the store. The store employees are either not paying attention or not around when I walk in. This is really annoying and it makes me late for work. It would be quicker to just walk in and order instead of using the app and ordering 10 minutes before! This is a constant trend at this location.
